# Public canonical URL of the deployed site. Used to build ABSOLUTE Open Graph
# URLs for link previews (LinkedIn, WhatsApp, X, Slack…). Open Graph requires an
# absolute URL, so set this to your real domain before deploying.
#
# On Vercel / Netlify the deploy URL is auto-detected if you leave this unset.
# Copy this file to `.env` (or set the var in your host) and adjust the value.
VITE_SITE_URL=https://tu-dominio.com
